commitResults.messageBody: Update repository in _config.yml
Add Use Case 1-4 in Developer Guide

Used Assisted refactoring to refactor the Address class into Location.

Location makes more sense in our target audience context since the
training location of the client is stored rather than the client's
address.

Labels in FXML elements are renamed to trainingLocation instead of just
location. The change in naming specifically in FXML is because
`location` is a reserved keyword in FXML.

Refer to this S/O discussion on the error
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/56247046/javafx-java-lang-illegalargumentexception-can-not-set-javafx-scene-control-labe
